title: Smart Trash v 1.1.6 + sn
description:
Official Web Site: <a href=" http://www.hyperbolicsoftware.com/SmartTrash.html" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.hyperbolicsoftware.com/SmartTrash.html</a>

Smart Trash enhances the functions of the Mac OS X trash by adding several menu options including: 

* selective file deletion

* extensive logging

* the ability to empty the trash on specific volumes

* and more.

What's new

Various bugs fixes from previous versions.

System Requirements:

Mac Intel OS version: 10.5.8 or later
